kgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為返學同返工有好多重要野都要用電腦做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好驚呢個問題會搞到啲重要file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d104411b18abc42478a04a5ca6cb132aa65802a0","tid":418391,"uid":135606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:43:00.000Z","msg":"求救自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16561375c730aaabd6ba1b9bf4264d8abcfe9f90","tid":418391,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:43:01.000Z","msg":"mac唔係唔會中毒咩"},{"pid":"aae551896cd35c16ddd4ebf51e812613a4f53cae","tid":418391,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2fac9fda662d29e4c9b2937f6c0485d4f3a12e","tid":418391,"uid":135606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:43:55.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14c6b261dbcc32c4cf3bfda680b496f0c7258d2","tid":418391,"uid":135606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:44:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>mac唔係唔會中毒咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想知點解"},{"pid":"e655313e6f4895a196891bcdb66a9fbbbbdbf281","tid":418391,"uid":104256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>mac唔係唔會中毒咩</blockquote><br />\n會 自己dl d 毒嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096b207fd3ca5d2af0802fa331e2f18839fc241a","tid":418391,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite